'''''Young Doctors''''' is an Australian [[factual television]] show that looks at the work of junior doctors at [[John Hunter Hospital]] in [[Newcastle, New South Wales]]. This eight-part observational documentary series began on the [[Nine Network]] on 26 October 2011. <ref>http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2011/09/young-doctors-sneak-peek.html</ref>
